verbose_text: In contrast to trans-10, cis-12 CLA effects in mice, SCD1 -/- mice showed increased insulin sensitivity, reduced hepatic lipogenic genes, upregulated lipid oxidizing genes, increased hepatic saturated FA and unchanged hepatic n-3 and n-6 PUFA [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: insulin sensitivity, reduced hepatic lipogenic genes, upregulated lipid oxidizing genes, increased hepatic saturated FA
